        <h2 style="margin-bottom:18px;">From proofs to predictions</h2>
        <p>I'm a final-year <strong>Mathematics</strong> student at Universitas Negeri Surabaya, currently finishing an undergraduate thesis that applies <strong>Kernel Extreme Learning Machine (K-ELM)</strong> models to forecast the stock price of a major Indonesian banking issuer at daily and weekly granularity.</p>
